1 Life expectancy in Madagascar

The average life expectancy in Madagascar between 1980 and 2010 was 53.71. The minimum life expectancy in Madagascar between 1980 and 2010 was 48.97. The maximum life expectancy in Madagascar between 1980 and 2010 was 59.44.
